   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>CONTENTS The Divine Dispensing and the Union and Mingling of the Triune God with the Believers The Divine Dispensing and the Increase of Christ The Proper Revelation concerning the Coming of Christ The Believers' Proper Attitude toward the Second Coming of Christ Distinctive Virtues of an Elder Laboring, Being Diligent, Striving, Struggling The Definite Steps to Practice the New Way Being Trained in the Divine Revelation Being Cultivated in the Divine Life Encouragement and Instructions for Those Participating in the Gospel Evangelization Work The Two Shortages and the Two Snares of Those Serving the Lord PREFACE</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>This book contains a series of messages given by Brother Witness Lee in Taipei, Taiwan in October 1990.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>Chapters one through four are messages given in a conference to the church in Taipei.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>Chapters five and six are messages given at the elders' and co-workers' meetings.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>Chapters seven and eight are messages given to the full-timers in the full-time training.</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>Chapters nine and ten are messages given to the full-time workers in the evangelizing work in the villages in Taiwan.</S>
